snippet: The Archdiocese of St. Paul and Minneapolis published a list on Thursday of 34 priests who have been accused of sexually abusing minors.
abstract: Archdiocese of St Paul and Minneapolis, under intense public pressure, publishes list of 34 priests who have been accused of sexually abusing minors.
lead_paragraph: The Archdiocese of St. Paul and Minneapolis published a list on Thursday of 34 priests who have been accused of sexually abusing minors.

headline.main: Minnesota: Archdiocese Releases Names of Priests Suspected of Abuse
headline.print_headline: Minnesota: Names of Suspect Priests Are Released
